flowchart TD
    A[Engine State / Event] --> B{Observation Need}

    B -->|Current condition| V[View]
    B -->|Action or transition evidence| R[Report]
    B -->|Abnormal condition| D[Diagnostic Report]

    V --> V1[Read-only projection]
    V --> V2[No mutation authority]
    V --> V3[Scope-bound]

    R --> R1[Immutable evidence]
    R --> R2[Transition/action trace]
    R --> R3[Does not expand authority]

    D --> D1[Classified condition]
    D --> D2[Severity]
    D --> D3[Owner / recovery hint]

    V1 --> C[Diagnostics / Tests / Approved Consumers]
    R1 --> C
    D1 --> C
